(7)European Reference Center Network (Euro-NMD ERN), Paris, France.
(8)Pediatric Neurology Department, AP-HP Hôpital Necker Enfants Malades, Paris, 
France.
(9)Department of Paediatric Neurology, Armand Trousseau Hospital, Assistance 
